                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1036-18500506 t18500506-1036-punishment-155"></join>Twice Whipped</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, JUNE</hi> 10<hi rend="smallCaps">TH</hi>, 1850.</p>
